<section class="philosophy reveal">
  <div class="container philosophy-inner">
    <div class="philosophy-text">
      <p class="fade-text">
        In Sanskrit, Setu (सेतु) means bridge —<br />
        connecting two shores without disturbing either.
      </p>
      <div class="separator"></div>
      <p class="fade-text delay-100">
        Good security should not require developer discipline.<br />
        The question of "Who committed this?" is no longer personal;<br />
        it is architectural.
      </p>
      <div class="separator"></div>
      <p class="philosophy-highlight delay-200">
        A tool that demands your attention has failed.<br />
        <span class="glow-text">GitSetu succeeds when you forget it exists.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .philosophy {
    background: transparent;
    padding-top: var(--space-5xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .philosophy-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .philosophy-text {
    max-width: 800px;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .fade-text {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: color var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .fade-text:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .separator {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.3), transparent);
    margin: var(--space-xl) auto;
  }

  .philosophy-highlight {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--text-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .glow-text {
    background: var(--gradient-accent);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 196, 204, 0.4);
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .philosophy-text {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }
    .philosophy-highlight {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
